{
    "text": "Have you been to Whitby Abbey? \ud83c\uddec\ud83c\udde7 \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642   It\u2019s an incredible UK landmark located on the Yorkshire Coast \ud83d\udccd   The atmosphere there is undeniable, with a history dating back to 657AD \ud83d\ude2f which is only increased with its connection with Dracula \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642   In 1890 Bram Stoker sat overlooking the Abbey ruins and it was their gothic charm that assisted his inspiration for the world-famous novel, Dracula \ud83e\udddb\u200d\u2642   Are you adding Whitby Abbey to your bucket list!? \u2728  #whitby #visityorkshire #visitwhitby #whitbyabbey #visitengland #thisprettyengland #travelengland #uktravel #traveluk #uktravels #uktraveller #uktrip #travelbucketlist #travelreel",
